('4701', '2', 'In a large nonstick skillet, heat the oil.'),
('4701', '3', 'Add the salmon and cook over moderately high heat, turning once, until browned but barely cooked through, about 6 minutes. Reduce the heat to moderate. add the chile and scallions. Cook until the scallions soften, about 2 minutes. Stir in the wine and water and simmer until the salmon is just cooked through, 1 minute. Stir in the basil.'),
('4701', '4', 'Transfer the salmon to plates and serve with rice and lime wedges.'),
