('4707', '2', 'Heat oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat.'),
('4707', '3', 'Add salmon, skin side down. cook 4 minutes on each side or until fish flakes easily with a fork or until desired degree of doneness. Arrange 1 fillet on each of 4 plates. Top fillets evenly with jalapeo slices. Spoon about 2 tablespoons soy sauce mixture over each serving. let stand 10 minutes before serving.'),
