('4708', '2', 'Brush fillets with oil.'),
('4708', '3', 'Place flesh side down on grill grate. Cook 5 to 6 minutes or until fillets can be lifted easily off grill without sticking to grate. Turn over with skin side down and cook 2 to 3 minutes more or until fish flakes easily with fork (145F).'),
('4708', '4', 'Transfer fillets to serving platter.'),
('4708', '5', 'Spoon 1 tablespoon sauce over each fillet.'),
('4708', '6', 'Serve remaining sauce on the side.'),
('4709', '1', 'Preheat oven to 40'),
('4709', '2', 'Combine first 4 ingredients in a small bowl. Sprinkle salmon evenly with salt and pepper. brush both sides of salmon with mustard mixture.'),
('4709', '3', 'Place potato flakes in a shallow dish. dredge salmon in potato flakes.'),
('4709', '4', 'Heat a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. Coat pan with cooking spray. Lightly spray salmon with cooking spray.'),
