('4710', '4', 'Combine honey, juice, soy sauce, and Sriracha. drizzle over fish. Sprinkle with green onions.'),
('4711', '1', 'Combine first 3 ingredients in a zip-top plastic bag. add salmon. Seal bag. marinate in refrigerator 30 minutes.'),
('4711', '2', 'Preheat oven to 50'),
